Package cz.itnetwork.entity

Class InvoiceEntity

java.lang.Object
cz.itnetwork.entity.InvoiceEntity
@Entity(name="invoice") public class InvoiceEntity extends Object
Represents an invoice within the system. This class is mapped to the invoice table in the database and contains various details related to the invoice.

The InvoiceEntity class includes fields such as:

  • id - Unique identifier for the invoice.
  • invoiceNumber - The number assigned to the invoice.
  • issued - The date when the invoice was issued.
  • dueDate - The date by which the invoice payment is due.
  • product - Description of the product or service invoiced.
  • price - The price of the product or service invoiced.
  • vat - The VAT rate applied to the invoice.
  • note - Additional notes or comments related to the invoice.
  • buyer - The person who is buying the product or service.
  • seller - The person who is selling the product or service.

The class uses Lombok annotations to automatically generate getters and setters for all fields.
